</li>
<li>
<p>Select a group under <strong>Send newsletter</strong> to group from the drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the option <strong>ALL</strong> or <strong>To confirmed email addresses only</strong> from the <strong>Filter</strong> drop-down list.</p>
</li>
