<p>You can use filters in CleverReach if you do not want to write to all customers whose data you have transferred to CleverReach. Further information can be found on the <a href="https://support.cleverreach.de/hc/en-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CleverReach</a> support page.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="2000">2.3. Manually transmitting customer data</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the <strong>Carry out data transfer</strong> option to only transfer customer data for a specific customer type. This allows you to sort the plentymarkets customer types into different CleverReach groups.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
