<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Should I use the automatic transfer?</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you use the option <strong>Carry out data transfer</strong> in order to transfer customer data filtered by customer type, you may have to deactivate the automatic transfer. The automatic transfer transfers all new customer data without considering the different customer types.</p>
</div>
</td>
